=== strokes

I didn't mean to write poetry.

I was just trying to keep the language economical.

Respecting the readers patience and leveraging their imagination.

Trying to keep them amused.

The style emerged organically.

* [Showcase: Into the Glinding Monkey] -> inn

=== inn

A roudy bunch freely taps giant barrels of mead, singing never-written songs.

Academic and labourer alike, cares at the door, honeyed heads abuzz.

The back opens to a backyard, somehow even noisier.

