=== palette

Rhyming is engaging.

Caveat: literal rhyming can be a bit pretentious and mentally taxing.

But thematic rhyming?

+ [Themes] -> themes

=== themes

A lean palette of themes:

* [Bees!] -> bees
* [Apes] -> apes
